<quantity box="[295,385,1719,1745]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="m" value="2200.0">2200 m</quantity>
a.s.l., 
<date box="[465,629,1719,1745]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1884-08-27">27 Aug. 1884</date>
, 
<emphasis box="[643,855,1719,1745]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">J.M. Delavay 197</emphasis>
[P212] (lecto-, designated here: P06811315!; isolecto-: B 10 0464027!, P06811316!, P06811317!, P06811318!, P06811319!, P06811320!, P06811321!, P06811335!, P06881735!). – Note: 
